kfi (Kernel Fabric Interface) provider for kernel OFA verbs (Infiniband/iWARP)

make			builds kifp-ibv provider
make clean		deletes all generated files
make load		loads kfip-ibv provider
make unload		unloads kfip-ibv provider
make info		modinfo kfip-ibv provider
make kcheck		find all loaded 'kfi' modules.
make help

to run a simple test,  cd to ../../tests/kfi/ibverbs/mm2 for a cli/svr test

develpment status:	pre-alpha
